          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1661880912510-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1661880912510-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced shallot</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Once slightly softened, add the<strong> pork mince</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up roughly with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1661880915776-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
