            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1661880920949-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork mince has browned, add the <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin </strong>and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to the pan with 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp] </span><strong>flour</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>cubed potatoes</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mix everything together until fully coated in spices and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
